{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Boolean 物件","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/orphaned/Web/JavaScript/Obsolete_Pages/Obsolete_Pages/Obsolete_Pages/預先定義的核心物件/Boolean_物件","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"boolean_物件","title":"Boolean 物件","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>Boolean</code> 物件是原始的 Boolean 資料類型包裝而成。使用下面的語法來建立 <code>Boolean</code> 物件︰</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">booleanObjectName = new Boolean(value)\n</pre>\n<p>別把原始的布林值的 <code>true</code> 和 <code>false</code> 與 <code>Boolean</code> 物件的 true 和 false 值給混淆了。任何物件的值只要不是 <code>undefined</code>、<code>null</code>、<code>0</code>、<code>NaN</code>、空字串，即使是值為 false 的 <code>Boolean</code> 物件，當傳入到條件語句裡的時候，其求值結果仍為 true。參閱 <a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_教學/條件語法#if...else_%e8%aa%9e%e6%b3%95\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 教學/條件語法#if...else 語法\">if...else 語法</a> 取得更進一步資訊。</p>\n<p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/預先定義的核心物件/Array_物件\">« 前頁</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/預先定義的核心物件/Date_物件\">次頁  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Boolean 物件是原始的 Boolean 資料類型包裝而成。使用下面的語法來建立 Boolean 物件︰","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","source":{"folder":"zh-tw/orphaned/web/javascript/obsolete_pages/obsolete_pages/obsolete_pages/預先定義的核心物件/boolean_物件","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/orphaned/web/javascript/obsolete_pages/obsolete_pages/obsolete_pages/預先定義的核心物件/boolean_物件/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"pageTitle":"Boolean 物件 | MDN","noIndexing":true}}